# ✅ ✅ Updated DevOps Python Modules List

***

# 🔷 Core System & Automation

* `os` → CPU count, env vars, system ops
* `sys` → exit codes, arguments, error handling
* `subprocess` → run shell commands (`ss`, `df`, `ps`)
* `shutil` → disk usage, file copy/move
* `psutil` → CPU, memory, disk, processes, network
* `pathlib` → modern file path handling
* `argparse` → CLI arguments for scripts
* `platform` → OS info (Linux/Windows detection)
* `getpass` → user/password handling

***

# 🔷 Networking & API Interaction

* `socket` → low-level network checks (TCP, ports)
* `ssl` → certificate validation, TLS checks
* `urllib` → basic HTTP calls (built-in)
* `requests` ✅ → REST APIs (MOST USED)
* `http.client` → low-level HTTP calls
* `paramiko` → SSH automation
* `fabric` → remote command execution
* `scp` → file transfer over SSH
* `dnspython (dns)` → DNS queries (A, MX, etc.)

***

# 🔷 Time & Scheduling

* `time` → sleep, timestamps
* `datetime` → date/time manipulation
* `sched` → basic scheduler
* `schedule` → cron-like jobs in Python
* `pytz` → timezone handling

***

# 🔷 Text Parsing & Config Handling

* `json` → API data parsing
* `re` → regex (logs, config parsing)
* `configparser` → `.ini` configs
* `csv` → CSV handling
* `yaml (PyYAML)` ✅ → YAML configs (K8s, Ansible)
* `toml` → modern configs (used in tools)
* `xml.etree.ElementTree` → XML parsing
* `jmespath` → query JSON (used with boto3)

***

